metadata.description: The avatar of DAO Moonopolis City is access to the distribution of income and management of the city of Moonopolis (Governing Council). This is the ownership of a part of the city. The avatar owner receives: Income from the sale of an ID card, manages the development of the city, income from the sale of DAO Moonopolis avatars, extended access to locations in the city. https://daomoonopolis.space
